title: Homemade Salami & Mozz Focaccia Pizza Made From Scratch Bread Series - roll up your sleeves!
description: When you have a little extra time (a great weekend project!), bake this from-scratch focaccia for homemade pizza you’ll be proud to show off! You’ll mix, rest, stretch the dough, top with marinara sauce, basil pesto, salami, and mozzarella, then bake until puffed and golden. Serve with a creamy balsamic-dressed green salad for a truly memorable meal.
